{
  "page": "Alfador",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Maester</span><br />Alfador</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/50px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/75px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/100px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">Hightower</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alfador</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> who served <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Hightower\" title=\"Hightower\">Hightower</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys I Targaryen\">Viserys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alfador&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After Grand Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Mellos\" title=\"Mellos\">Mellos</a> passed away, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> recommended that her own maester, <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a>, take his place as Grand Maester. Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alicent_Hightower\" title=\"Alicent Hightower\">Alicent Hightower</a>, on the other hand, wanted Maester Alfador named to the office. Beset from both sides, King Viserys chose neither, reminding both his wife and daughter that the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> would decide who filled the office. Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Orwyle\" title=\"Orwyle\">Orwyle</a>, in the end, was selected by the conclave as the new Grand Maester.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alfador&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Heirs of the Dragon - A Question of Succession.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403203009\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.063 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.236 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 516/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10432/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5983/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 824/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1125/5000000 byt